{"id":441256,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":14}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"科学教育电影展览专辑","genre":"","count":"437","ytitle":"","mtitle":"科学教育电影展览专辑","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>刘咏</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020801.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>《知识老人》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知识老人谈天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流星、极光、风云、雷雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然飞来气球传信息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问道空气秘密。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020802.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>《巧种多收》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸清庄稼脾气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧妙安排邻居，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉米大豆最亲密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和和睦睦两兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个高，一个低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通风透光都有利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃、喝、住，两相宜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不争肥料不争地。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020803.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020804.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>《任伯年的画》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代大师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩笔传神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擅长人物、花鸟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别具风格。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布局新颖、构图灵巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尤善用颜色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳叶停蝉,"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姿态何等生动活泼。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020805.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>《斜面》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜面斜面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本领通天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举重如轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登高不难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜面斜面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变化多端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能劈能钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入地上天。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020806.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>《奇峰异洞》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青莲出水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万石成林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峡谷伏流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洞中水落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此奇峰异洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁雕塑?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水!千年万年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在石灰岩层工作。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1963\\03\\633e020807.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>洪德顺,李世顺</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>《金小蜂与红铃虫》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大自然有多少奥秘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凶恶的害虫也有天敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身小体微的金小蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟能消灭棉花的大敌——红铃虫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金小蜂挥动它的武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产卵管刺进红铃虫身体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茧子变成育儿室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有吃、有喝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么惬意!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红铃虫被吸干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二代金小蜂又生出羽翼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本版配诗　刘咏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"配图　洪德顺　李杨均</FONT>"}]}